2003-07-18 17:17  flo

	* src/core/: ConfigurationParser.cxx, Context.cxx, Context.h,
	Node.cxx:
	
	adding namespace support to OpenTracker! this should be transparent
	for existing applications and configfiles, but gives you the
	possibility to use namespaces in OpenTracker files when using a
	schema to validate.  Note that the namespaces are not supported
	when using the DTD!

